{"ID":270354, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"354\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs353.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs355.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 354<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I want to reason more on the spirit of man;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> for I am dwelling on the body and spirit of\n  man<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span>&mdash;on the subject of the dead. I take my ring from my finger and liken it unto the mind of\n  man&mdash;the immortal part,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> because it has no beginning. Suppose you cut it in two; then it has a\n  beginning and an end; but join it again, and it continues one eternal round.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> So with the spirit of man.\n  As the Lord liveth, if it had a beginning, it will have an end. All the fools and learned and wise men\n  from the beginning of creation,<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> who say that the spirit of man had a beginning, prove that it must\n  have an end; and if that doctrine is true, then the doctrine of annihilation would be true. But if I am\n  right, I might with boldness proclaim from the house-tops<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> that God never had the power to create\n  the spirit of man<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> at all. God himself could not create himself.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Intelligence is eternal<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> and exists upon a self-existent principle. It is a spirit<span class=\"textFootRef\">a<\/span> from age to age,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span>\n  and there is no creation about it. All the minds and spirits that God ever sent into the world are\n  susceptible of enlargement.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Power to Advance in Knowledge<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The first principles of man are self-existent with God. God himself, finding he was in the midst\n  of spirits and glory,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> because he was more intelligent,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> saw proper to institute laws whereby the\n  rest could have a privilege to advance like himself.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> The relationship we have with God places us\n  in a situation to advance in knowledge.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> He has power to institute laws to instruct the weaker\n  intelligences,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> that they may be exalted with himself,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> so that they might have one glory upon\n  another,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> and all that knowledge, power, glory,<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and intelligence, which is requisite in order to save\n  them in the world of spirits.<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span><span class=\"textFootRef\">,b<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106613\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106613)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106613)\">Job 32:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109956\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109956)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109956)\">1 Thes. 5:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112857\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112857)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112857)\">Ether 3:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114810\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114810)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114810)\">D&amp;C 88:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117075\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117075)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117075)\">Abr. 5:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111199\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111199)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111199)\">2 Ne. 9:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110960\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110960)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110960)\">1 Ne. 10:19<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111835\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111835)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111835)\">Alma 7:20<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112210\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112210)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112210)\">Alma 37:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113101\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113101)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113101)\">D&amp;C 3:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113599\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113599)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113599)\">D&amp;C 35:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108349\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108349)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108349)\">Mark 10:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115691\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115691)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115691)\">D&amp;C 112:31<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116414\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116414)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116414)\">D&amp;C 132:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112779\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112779)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112779)\">Morm. 5:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115033\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115033)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115033)\">D&amp;C 93:29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115034\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115034)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115034)\">D&amp;C 93:29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116564\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116564)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116564)\">D&amp;C 135:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112117\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112117)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112117)\">Alma 32:34<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117045\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117045)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117045)\">Abr. 3:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117036\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117036)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117036)\">Abr. 3:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108660\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108660)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108660)\">John 3:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108879\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108879)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108879)\">John 17:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109735\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109735)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109735)\">Gal. 3:24-25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111375\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111375)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111375)\">Jacob 2:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114552\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114552)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114552)\">D&amp;C 78:4<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116740\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116740)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116740)\">Moses 1:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114840\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114840)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114840)\">D&amp;C 88:40-41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116969\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116969)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116969)\">Abr. 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114955\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114955)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114955)\">D&amp;C 89:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108795\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108795)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108795)\">John 14:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108880\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108880)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108880)\">John 17:22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117052\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117052)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117052)\">Abr. 3:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110494\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110494)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110494)\">2 Pet. 1:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116676\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116676)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116676)\">D&amp;C 138:36,56-57<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n  <div class=\"textFootnotes\">\n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">a<\/span>&ldquo;A spirit from age to age&rdquo;&mdash;not &ldquo;spirit from age to age&rdquo;;\n        but &ldquo;a spirit,&rdquo; that is, an entity, a person, an individual. This paragraph in the Prophet&rsquo;s remarks may well be taken as an interpretation of Doc. and Cov., Sec. 93:29.&mdash;Note by Elder B. H. Roberts.<\/p>\n    \n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">b<\/span>&ldquo;Behold this is my work and my glory&mdash;to bring to pass the immortality and eternal life of man.&rdquo;&mdash;(The Lord to Moses, Book of Moses, chapt. 1:39, Pearl of Great Price)&mdash;that is, &ldquo;to bring to pass the immortality and eternal life of man, as man. The passage has reference doubtless to man as composed of spirit and body&mdash;a proper &ldquo;soul&rdquo; (see Doc. and Cov. Sec. 88:15-16)&mdash;&ldquo;For the spirit and the body is the soul of man;\n        and the resurrection of the dead is the redemption of the soul.&rdquo; In other words, the &ldquo;work&rdquo; and the &ldquo;glory&rdquo; of God are achieved in bringing to pass the &ldquo;immortality and eternal life of man,&rdquo; as man, in the eternal union of the spirit and body of man through the resurrection through the redemption of the soul. This<\/p>\n    \n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}